### Login
POST {{MinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Weather Forecast (Requires Authorization)
GET {{MinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/WeatherForecast
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Accept: application/json

